{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014sXaAkLJ9Y3Ynnoaji93ca","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration is complete and fully verified. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Migration approach:** Configured RabbitMQ's built-in Shovel plugin (already enabled on the green cluster) to pull messages from blue to green.\n\n**Steps executed:**\n1. Verified blue had 50 messages (IDs 1..50), green had 0\n2. Confirmed cross-namespace AMQP connectivity from green → blue\n3. Created a dynamic shovel on the green cluster (`/api/parameters/shovel/%2Fapp/blue-to-green`) with:\n   - Source: `amqp://app:apppass@rabbitmq-blue.<source-ns>.svc.cluster.local/%2Fapp`, queue `app-queue`\n   - Destination: `amqp://app:apppass@localhost/%2Fapp`, queue `app-queue`\n   - `src-delete-after: queue-length` — moves exactly the current queue depth (50) then terminates\n4. Shovel completed automatically (returned empty `[]` on status check after completion)\n\n**Result:**\n- Green `/app/app-queue`: **50 messages, IDs 1–50, no gaps**\n- Blue `/app/app-queue`: **0 messages** (traffic cut — blue is drained, green is ready for consumers)"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":318,"cache_read_input_tokens":44991,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":318},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"75acee1f-dede-4bf4-b616-a75525bc7bdc","uuid":"1de405bd-b6a4-4de4-9135-ca3e4103e73a","request_id":"req_011CcRLHnnH2X3fbvj2bJPrt"}
